    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Description</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Descend into ancient ruins that were never meant to be uncovered.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the walls shift and whispers grow louder, you realize something is watching — and not everyone who enters will escape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4312090/extras/984873e5381e7b057504a59573a070e1.poster.avif?t=1772017074\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4312090/extras/984873e5381e7b057504a59573a070e1.webm?t=1772017074\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4312090/extras/984873e5381e7b057504a59573a070e1.mp4?t=1772017074\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >According to forgotten legends, disturbing these ruins stirs an ancient presence bound to stone and blood. As the corridors shift and whispers echo through the darkness, escape becomes uncertain—and survival comes at a terrible cost.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>Marzu</strong>, you play as an explorer driven to uncover the truth behind the ruins and the force that dwells within them.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gameplay</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Marzu</strong> is a first-person survival horror game focused on exploration, environmental storytelling, and psychological tension. You will navigate collapsing corridors, decipher ancient symbols, and solve disturbing puzzles while the ruins react to your presence.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4312090/extras/1f65ab2c89209d31cb8d8d639d87878c.poster.avif?t=1772017074\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4312090/extras/1f65ab2c89209d31cb8d8d639d87878c.webm?t=1772017074\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4312090/extras/1f65ab2c89209d31cb8d8d639d87878c.mp4?t=1772017074\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you progress, the environment becomes increasingly hostile passageways change, sounds distort, and an unseen presence stalks you through the darkness. Resources are limited, every decision matters, and fear is built through atmosphere rather than constant combat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4312090/extras/bd0c3bfefeb60144790f4ec50cf80813.poster.avif?t=1772017074\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4312090/extras/bd0c3bfefeb60144790f4ec50cf80813.webm?t=1772017074\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4312090/extras/bd0c3bfefeb60144790f4ec50cf80813.mp4?t=1772017074\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Atmosphere</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Realistic lighting, detailed ancient architecture, and immersive 3D sound design bring the ruins of <strong>Marzu</strong> to life. Every echo, distant whisper, and shifting stone is designed to keep you on edge as the ruins close in around you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4312090/extras/a7568d1dd2054982e54ba4cce5013017.poster.avif?t=1772017074\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4312090/extras/a7568d1dd2054982e54ba4cce5013017.webm?t=1772017074\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4312090/extras/a7568d1dd2054982e54ba4cce5013017.mp4?t=1772017074\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FEATURES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Explore shifting ancient ruins filled with secrets</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Solve environmental puzzles and decipher symbols</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Survive limited resources and growing psychological tension</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Experience dynamic sound and unsettling encounters</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Uncover a dark truth buried beneath stone and blood</p>",
